      "text": "…One of the components of [[Biophilic Urbanism]] is concerned with how attractive we perceive surfaces to be when we are near them. Then, [[Human-Scale Detail]] can help to define surfaces that we can connect with. Lastly, [[Complex Materials]] offer far more visual interest, hence emotional engagement, than dull industrial materials.",
